Objective:
Build an incremental per-talent qualitative monetary-relationship analysis from raw text logs only.

This workflow is meant to understand:
- why chat appears to give money
- what kinds of streamer behavior or interaction patterns appear to attract money
- how paid moments function relationally between streamer and chat

This workflow must not rely on any other derived analysis products yet. It is intentionally independent from summary-classification, personality, title, analytics, demographic, and bundle workflows.

Scope rules:
- Process every talent folder directly under the data root that contains either `text_playback/` or `Chat/Original/`.
- Skip the aggregate folder `VarianceProject`.
- Do not process only one talent unless explicitly instructed.

